data.description: You do not want to miss this charming all brick home, located just one mile from Downtown Kannapolis!!! This home has been beautifully renovated and offers three bedrooms, two full bathrooms with an open floor plan. The rocking chair front porch gives the perfect touch to this charming home and don't forget about the fully fenced back yard that adds extra privacy. As an added bonus the sellers loan is assumable so please reach out for additional details. The sellers will be leaving the Washer, Dryer and Refrigerator.
